Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.input

Interface InputService

All Superinterfaces:
Insertion, TableFilter, TableInsertion
All Known Implementing Classes:
InputServiceImpl
public interface InputService extends Insertion, TableInsertion, TableFilter
Provides service-level methods for interacting with input UI components.

This interface defines operations for inserting, clearing, retrieving values, and verifying the state of input fields, delegating the actual interactions to specific implementations based on the configured InputComponentType.
